==================================================
dust meter 01
==================================================
= Copyright (c) Davide Gironi, 2013              =
= http://davidegironi.blogspot.it/               =
==================================================


This project is a dust meter that use the GP2Y1010AU0F sensor.
GP2Y1010AU0F is a dust sensor by optical sensing system. An infrared emitting
diode (IRED) and an phototransistor are diagonally arranged into this device.
It detects the reflected light of dust in air. Especially, it is effective
to detect very fine particle like the cigarette smoke.


Devel Notes
-----------
This library was developed on Eclipse, built with avr-gcc on Atmega8 @ 8MHz.


